'''A Utopian Tree Sapling with a height of 1 inch is plated on day1. The tree grows 2 inches every day.Find the height of the tree in centimeters on nth day. (HINT: 1 inch= 2.54 cms)

input:n day
output:height in cms'''

days=int(input("enter no.of days: "))
tree_height=1*2.5
day_height=days*5+1*2.5
print(f'Utopian Tree Height initialy = {1*2.5}cms\nThe tree grows every day = {2*2.5}cms\n The Height of Tree for {days} days = {day_height}cms')

